    "created_at": "2016-05-30T16:03:02Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-05-30T16:16:39Z",
    "body": "Just one issue. How we you supposed to account for the fact that titleBarStyle doesn't work for OSX Mavericks?\n\nIf we have to include custom HTML component to act as a draggable menu in Yosemite+, then we have to _not include_ that same html component for OSX Mavericks, or else for OSX Mavericks we'll have two menu bars. How can we achieve this without having to create two separate builds? \n"
